name: places/ChIJMQ-TQwIa2jERQ_5C9MU5bkg/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTURnekxXdkNBEAE
text:
{'text': 'A decent stadium equipped with an American football field, a 6 lane running track, car park via the Ministry of Education, some sheltered seating and toilets.

The fields are well maintained, but the running tracks are slightly dilapidated at the time of writing (Feb 2025)

The field is publicly available 24/7. While the field lights are not turned on at nights, the ambient lights provide some lighting for late night and early morning activities.

The toilets are a little outdated, but well equipped with showers, changing areas, and are well maintained.', 'languageCode': 'en'}

text: {'text': 'Track is in need of repairs.
